com.github.gwtbootstrap.client.ui

Class CollapseTrigger

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.gwtbootstrap.client.ui.base.MarkupWidget
      • com.github.gwtbootstrap.client.ui.CollapseTrigger
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasId, AcceptsOneWidget, HasOneWidget, HasWidgets, IsWidget, Iterable<Widget>

    public class CollapseTrigger
extends MarkupWidget
    Markup widget of CollapseTrigger

    It's a markup widget (decorator widget). it's can exchange child to Collapse's toggle trigger widget.

    UiBinder Usage:

     <b:CollapseTrigger target="#toggle1">
      <b:Button>Collapse Trigger</b:Button>
 </b:CollapseTrigger>

 <!-- if use collapse trigger, you must set existTrigger=true attribute to Collapse tag. -->
 <b:Collapse existTrigger="true" b:id="toggle1" defaultOpen="true">
     <b:FluidRow>
         <b:Column size="12">
             <b:Alert close="false" animation="true" heading="collapsible1">
                 <b:Paragraph>
                     Hello :D
                 </b:Paragraph>
             </b:Alert>
         </b:Column>
     </b:FluidRow>
 </b:Collapse>
    Since:
    2.2.1.0
    Author:
    ohashi keisuke
    See Also:
    Accordion, Collapse, CollapseTrigger, Twitter Bootstrap document
